updated vesrion of the program

-fixed a few bugs
-sperated and better organized the the three programs for chess board cropping


To use this program first you have to download all athe files in one one folder then you have 4 options:

1-open and run Thresholding_and_Contouring to crop the image using Thresholding and then find board using the largest contour

2-open and run Canny_edge_and_Hough_Lines to crom the image using canny edge detector and Hough lines

3- (recommended) for the best results use Shi_Tomasi_Corners to crop the image using modified Harris corner algorithm 

4- (recommended) for the best results use live_cam_and_Shi_Tomasi_Cropping to crop to crop a live vedio of a chess board with reasonable 
    accuracy

